title: Jessica Jaymes' Cause of Death Deferred After Adult Film Star's Autopsy
text:
The autopsy on porn star Jessica Jaymes has been completed, but investigators need to wait on more tests in order to determine exactly how the starlet died.

Officials have listed her death as "deferred" pending the toxicity report once all the results come in from the lab.

As we reported, 43-year-old Jaymes was found dead Tuesday at her home after her ex-husband became worried after she had not responded to calls.

Law enforcement sources told The Blast emergency services received a call at 4:15 PM on Tuesday for an unconscious and unresponsive female at a home in the San Fernando Valley.

View photos

Jaymes was pronounced dead at the scene, and sources familiar with the ongoing death investigation told us Jaymes had a history of seizures.

Multiple prescription medication bottles were collected at the scene for testing, but it's unclear if they played a part in her death.
